<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="page-header">
    <h1>Account Appeal</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Request a review of your account suspension or ban</p>
</div>

<div class="content-section">
    <div class="appeal-intro">
        <h2>About Account Appeals</h2>
        <p>If your account was suspended or banned and you believe this was an error, you can submit an appeal. We take account actions seriously and will carefully review your case.</p>
        
        <div class="appeal-types">
            <div class="appeal-type-card">
                <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Temporary Suspension</h3>
                <p>Your account is temporarily restricted. You can appeal if you believe this was in error or want to provide context.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="appeal-type-card">
                <h3>üö´ Permanent Ban</h3>
                <p>Your account has been permanently disabled. Appeals are reviewed for severe policy violations or mistaken identity.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="important-notice">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> Creating additional accounts to bypass a ban may result in permanent IP blocking. Please use this appeal process instead.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="appeal-form-wrapper">
        <form class="appeal-form" action="/api/appeals/account" method="POST">
            <div class="form-row">
                <label for="email" class="form-label">Account Email Address</label>
                <input 
                    type="email" 
                    id="email" 
                    name="email" 
                    class="form-input" 
                    placeholder="email@example.com"
                    required 
                />
                <small class="hint">The email associated with your Dream X account</small>
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
                <label for="username" class="form-label">Username/Handle</label>
                <input 
                    type="text" 
                    id="username" 
                    name="username" 
                    class="form-input" 
                    placeholder="@yourusername"
                    required 
                />
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
                <label for="accountAction" class="form-label">Type of Account Action</label>
                <select id="accountAction" name="accountAction" class="form-input" required>
                    <option value="">Select action type...</option>
                    <option value="temporary-suspension">Temporary Suspension</option>
                    <option value="permanent-ban">Permanent Ban</option>
                    <option value="feature-restriction">Feature Restriction</option>
                    <option value="shadow-ban">Shadow Ban (Suspected)</option>
                    <option value="other">Other/Unknown</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
                <label for="actionDate" class="form-label">When did this happen? (approximate)</label>
                <input 
                    type="date" 
                    id="actionDate" 
                    name="actionDate" 
                    class="form-input" 
                />
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
                <label for="violationReason" class="form-label">Reason Given (if known)</label>
                <select id="violationReason" name="violationReason" class="form-input">
                    <option value="">Select if you know...</option>
                    <option value="spam">Spam/Bot Activity</option>
                    <option value="harassment">Harassment or Bullying</option>
                    <option value="hate-speech">Hate Speech</option>
                    <option value="impersonation">Impersonation</option>
                    <option value="multiple-violations">Multiple Policy Violations</option>
                    <option value="illegal-activity">Illegal Activity</option>
                    <option value="evasion">Ban Evasion</option>
                    <option value="copyright">Copyright Violations</option>
                    <option value="other">Other/Unknown</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
                <label for="appealReason" class="form-label">Why do you believe this action was incorrect?</label>
                <textarea 
                    id="appealReason" 
                    name="appealReason" 
                    rows="6" 
                    class="form-textarea" 
                    placeholder="Please provide a detailed explanation of why you believe the account action was made in error. Include any relevant context, explanations, or information that might help us review your case..."
                    required
                ></textarea>
                <small class="hint">Be honest and specific. Provide any evidence that supports your case.</small>
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
                <label for="preventionPlan" class="form-label">If violations occurred, how will you prevent them in the future?</label>
                <textarea 
                    id="preventionPlan" 
                    name="preventionPlan" 
                    rows="5" 
                    class="form-textarea" 
                    placeholder="Describe the steps you'll take to comply with our Community Guidelines if your account is restored..."
                ></textarea>
                <small class="hint">This shows you understand our policies and are committed to following them.</small>
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
                <label for="additionalInfo" class="form-label">Additional Context (optional)</label>
                <textarea 
                    id="additionalInfo" 
                    name="additionalInfo" 
                    rows="4" 
                    class="form-textarea" 
                    placeholder="Any other information that might help us review your appeal (compromised account, mistaken identity, etc.)..."
                ></textarea>
            </div>

            <div class="form-row">
                <label for="contactEmail" class="form-label">Contact Email (if different from account email)</label>
                <input 
                    type="email" 
                    id="contactEmail" 
                    name="contactEmail" 
                    class="form-input" 
                    placeholder="alternative@email.com"
                />
                <small class="hint">Where we should send the appeal decision</small>
            </div>

            <div class="appeal-notice">
                <p><strong>Before submitting your appeal:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Review our <a href="/community-guidelines">Community Guidelines</a> and <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a></li>
                    <li>Be honest about any violations that may have occurred</li>
                    <li>Understand that some violations may not be reversible</li>
                    <li>Do not create additional accounts while your appeal is pending</li>
                    <li>Submitting false information may result in permanent account termination</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="form-actions">
                <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">Cancel</a>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Submit Appeal</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="appeal-info">
        <h2>Appeal Review Process</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-number">1</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Appeal Received</h3>
                    <p>You'll receive an email confirmation with a case number to track your appeal</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-number">2</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Investigation</h3>
                    <p>Our team reviews your account history, the violation, and your appeal explanation</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-number">3</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Decision</h3>
                    <p>We make a decision based on our policies and the evidence provided (typically within 3-5 business days)</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-number">4</div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <h3>Notification</h3>
                    <p>You'll receive our decision via email with an explanation and any next steps</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>How long does the appeal process take?</h3>
                <p>Most appeals are reviewed within 3-5 business days. Complex cases may take longer.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>Can I submit multiple appeals?</h3>
                <p>You can submit one appeal per account action. If your appeal is denied, you may request a final review after 30 days.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What happens if my appeal is approved?</h3>
                <p>Your account will be restored with full access. In some cases, you may receive a warning or temporary restrictions.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>What if my appeal is denied?</h3>
                <p>We'll explain the reason for denial. Decisions are final unless new evidence becomes available.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>My account was compromised. What should I do?</h3>
                <p>Mention this in your appeal and provide any evidence (unusual login locations, times, etc.). We take account security seriously.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

